# Azure credentials/config for local deployments (DO NOT COMMIT the real file)
#
# 1) Copy this file to: azure/env.azure
# 2) Fill in values as needed
# 3) Run: ./azure/deploy.sh ... (scripts auto-load azure/env.azure)
#
# This repo's root .gitignore ignores `secrets/`, `*.key`, `*.pem`, and `.env.*`.
# NOTE: If you prefer `.env.azure`, it's also ignored by `azure/.env*` in the root .gitignore.

# --------------------------------------------
# Authentication (Service Principal) - optional
# --------------------------------------------
# If these are set and you're not already logged in, scripts will run:
# az login --service-principal -u $AZURE_CLIENT_ID -p $AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET --tenant $AZURE_TENANT_ID
#
# AZURE_TENANT_ID=
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID=

# --------------------------------------------
# Defaults (optional)
# --------------------------------------------
# AZURE_RESOURCE_GROUP=canada-agent-rg
# AZURE_LOCATION=eastus
# AZURE_ACR_NAME=canadaagent
# AZURE_IMAGE_TAG=latest

